BOOLEAN CamWin32::SetTwilightModeEnabled (  BOOLEAN  twilight_mode  ) 
 

Enables or disables the twilight mode. This increases the sensitivity of the camera's imaging sensor. If the camera does not support a twilight mode, this does not have an effect and FALSE is returned.

Parameters:

Returns:
